    <!-- Comma separated list of domain:level pairs to specify log level
       - thresholds for domains. Domain could be 'dactl', the name of a plugin,
       - or '*' for all. Allowed levels are:
       -  1 (critical)
       -  2 (error)
       -  3 (warning)
       -  4 (message/info)
       -  5 (debug)
       -->
